<section>
	<h2 id="example">Example usage</h2>
	<p>All the styles are available not only as atomic classes, but also as SCSS variables (see wds-variables/typography), so that you can merge them into your other style rules.</p>
	{{#code-sample language='scss'}}
body {
	font-family: $wds-font-family;
	line-height: $wds-line-height-none;
}

.wds-component {
	font-size: $wds-font-size-base;
}
	{{/code-sample}}
</section>
